videos.headline: Jefferson bolts 54 yards for Oregon State TD
videos.description: Jermar Jefferson takes the handoff and jets down the field to score a 54-yard Oregon State touchdown in the first quarter.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Jefferson bolts 54 yards for Oregon State TD) 2019/11/23 ESHEET

videos.headline: Washington State's Patmon stretches out to score 12-yard TD
videos.description: Dezmon Patmon makes the catch and stretches out to reach the end zone to score a 12-yard Washington State touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Washington State's Patmon stretches out to score 12-yard TD) 2019/11/23 ESHEET

videos.headline: Luton completes deep pass to Flemings for 46-yard Beavers TD
videos.description: Jake Luton rifles a pass deep for Champ Flemings, who makes the catch and dives into the end zone to score a 46-yard Oregon State touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Luton completes deep pass to Flemings for 46-yard Beavers TD) 2019/11/23 ESHEET

videos.headline: Washington State's McIntosh scoots 33 yards to the end zone
videos.description: Anthony Gordon throws a shovel pass to Deon McIntosh who navigates 33 yards to score a Washington State touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Washington State's McIntosh scoots 33 yards to the end zone) 2019/11/23 ESHEET

videos.headline: Washington State's Gordon ties Pac-12 single season record for TD passes
videos.description: Anthony Gordon completes a pass to Calvin Jackson Jr. who treks into the end zone to score a 36-yard touchdown and give Washington State a 28-24 lead over Oregon State.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Washington State's Gordon ties Pac-12 single season record for TD passes) 2019/11/23 ESHEET

videos.headline: Gordon breaks Pac-12 record with 44th TD pass of the season
videos.description: Anthony Gordon throws a 10-yard touchdown pass to Renard Bell to record his 44th touchdown pass of the season and break the Pac-12 record for most touchdown passes in a single season.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Gordon breaks Pac-12 record with 44th TD pass of the season) 2019/11/23 ESHEET

videos.headline: Oregon State retakes the lead on Jefferson's 39-yard TD
videos.description: Oregon State takes a 46-42 lead over Washington State as Jake Luton completes a pass to Jermar Jefferson, who gets into the end zone to score a 39-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Oregon State retakes the lead on Jefferson's 39-yard TD) 2019/11/23 ESHEET

videos.headline: Washington State scores last-second TD for the win
videos.description: Max Borghi runs it in from the two-yard line to score a Washington State touchdown and give them a 54-53 lead with two seconds left in the game.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Washington State scores last-second TD for the win) 2019/11/23 ESHEET
